{"tid":1938350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：因湖北省的疫情最近轉趨緩和 專機回港居民只需接受14日家居檢疫","createTime":"2020-03-22T13:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T14:04:22.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2210b5ef8a372329765e3d36ec2c31d2734cf8e3","tid":1938350,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"特區政府調整派遣專機接回滯留湖北港人的行動部署<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  ...特區政府為今次第二批專機接載行動作出有關調整，是經詳細審視目前內地的疫情和香港的最新情況，以及衡量香港的公共衞生風險，目的是盡最大努力接回滯留湖北希望回港的香港居民，同時確保香港的防疫和醫療系統有足夠的承載能力。<br />\n   <br />\n  有關調整主要有兩方面。<span style=\"color: red;\">第一，湖北省的疫情最近轉趨緩和，在徵詢公共衞生專家的意見後，特區政府將要求從武漢市以外、由湖北省其他地區回港的香港居民接受十四天家居檢疫</span>。<br />\n   <br />\n  同時，所有為第一批接載行動作出的防禦措施，包括健康評估、湖北省政府對乘搭專機的港人的確診核查，以及登機前多次的體溫檢測，將會繼續進行。若出現發燒、健康表徵不正常、呼吸道病徵或其他傳染病徵狀，將不能乘坐專機。<br />\n   <br />\n  第二、由於武漢仍然被當地政府評為高風險地區，根據專家意見，從武漢市回來的人士仍然須要入住檢疫中心接受十四天的檢疫。鑑於香港的輸入個案激增，檢疫中心必須預留足夠的單位，處理預計迅速增加的確診者的緊密接觸個案，以及可能出現的突發情況。<span style=\"color: red;\">因此，今次行動將不會包括在武漢市內的新增求助個案</span>。...<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/21/P2020032100672.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202003%2F21%2FP2020032100672.htm&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdFznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=209b9d88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202003/21/P2020032100672.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bbed3b43898456636bf48a160ceaa8e10411205","tid":1938350,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addb53a951647dcdd0fb0a71ec9b81af39a1cf81","tid":1938350,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"武漢都開始解封,仲包機黎做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f27e4b353008d430a330b5edb1f59dae6f3504a","tid":1938350,"uid":158457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"而家香港危險過武漢呀<br />\n唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef432820bdc640a0731adddf21ff09e694af16d","tid":1938350,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9927d735f07a6834c1f5d11588e623b34e487a1","tid":1938350,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc19274f34796c0c0842cadf8b8b3e07299078e","tid":1938350,"uid":195821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"湖北 0 確䂦，全球最安全，點解要黎香港呢個疫區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f5c53a66f70a4556d47847b008b7d9fe8d13ba","tid":1938350,"uid":337899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fc19274f34796c0c0842cadf8b8b3e07299078e","tid":1938350,"uid":195821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:25:53.000Z","msg":"湖北 0 確䂦，全球最安全，點解要黎香港呢個疫區<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:26:39.000Z","msg":"點解尋日冇記者問?"},{"pid":"40424ac9991cad458c54c4e49ffffd202426e939","tid":1938350,"uid":25525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"返黎中咗都唔可以公佈"},{"pid":"63aef0db9caf17e5a05cb5640646c09394e63a8d","tid":1938350,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,